# Findings
- **Main Page URL:** https://lmstudio.ai/
- **Windows Download Button:** Present on the main page.
- **Default Port:** 1234 (Confirmed in Documentation: https://lmstudio.ai/docs/developer/rest/quickstart)
- **Installation Steps:**
  1. Go to https://lmstudio.ai/ and click "Download LM Studio for Windows".
  2. Run the downloaded `.exe` file to install.
  3. Open LM Studio.
  4. Go to the "Local Server" tab (represented by a double-arrow icon `<->` or similar, labeled "Developer" in some versions).
  5. Select a model to load.
  6. Click "Start Server" to enable the API on `http://localhost:1234`.
